  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Supervise and coordinate the construction site to ensure daily site work targets are met.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monitor site processes and resolve any issues to minimize downtime.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that all safety and quality standards are adhered to.</li>\n  <li>Provide guidance and training to site workers.</li>\n  <li>Implement and enforce operational procedures to improve efficiency and reduce waste.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and maintain project reports.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with other departments to ensure smooth operations and resolve any issues.</li>\n  <li>Identify opportunities for process improvements and implement necessary changes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience as a construction Supervisor .</li>\n  <li>Excellent leadership and team management skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to troubleshoot and resolve site-related issues.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and organizational skills.</li>\n  <li>High school or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
